</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I'm sick of this shit (non-EQ rant)</span><hr size=1> /applaud Tyras..Isn't it nice to be able to view the world through the eyes of common sense and a strong knowledge of what is right and what is wrong?<br>
<br>
As far as these child killers go and any other crime against humanity for that matter,(i.e. kidnapping, rape and other sex crimes, murder) , I know that if it is ever to end, the people have to demand that this weak lack of a justice system be toughened up.<br>
<br>
The Solution is as follows:<br>
<br>
1.  If a person commits a capitol crime(murder, sexual molestation, rape) then that person should be put to death via hanging.  The family of the victim should be able to participate in the execution and rope/big trees doesn't cost the taxpayers out the arse.<br>
<br>
2. Televise all executions to the general public.  The media wants to cover something and dwell on these sick bastards, then let them dwell on their executions.<br>
<br>
3. For crimes like robbery, assault and domestic violence(without severe physical damage), and all other lesser crimes, the criminals should be punished in a public forum as well.  I propose putting them in stocks in the most crowded square of the community in which they commited the crime, and letting all of the citizens walk by and watch as they get caned by law enforcement officials.  Their crime would be posted on a sign right next to their restraint device.<br>
<br>
<br>
The bottom line is this, I and I'm sure you all too, am sick and damn tired of paying taxes that go towards keeping these wastes of good air in prison with amenities.  Most prisoners have cable television, 3 meals a day(not slop either), a comfortable place to sleep, FULL medical care, sports and recreational facilities, and a FREE education.  This amounts to about 40k dollars per year, PER INMATE, to provide them with all of these luxuries.  Hell, Navy personnel at sea do not live as good as these guys do and that is Bullshit.<br>
<br>
<br>
If we are to keep this joke of a prison and &quot;so called&quot; rehabilitation system, then ATLEAST MAKE IT AN UNDESIRABLE PLACE TO BE.<br>
<br>
<br>
/rant off<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Zephyris<br>
